                    	<note xml:id="n_dating" type="dating">
                    	    
<p>When Vincent wrote this letter, <ref target="let196.xml">letter 196</ref> of on or about 3 January 1882 had already been sent, though he had not yet received Theo’s letter of 5 January (<ref target="let197.xml">letter 197</ref>) (see <ref target="#l-21">ll. 21-23</ref>). That letter probably arrived on 6 January, or possibly 7 January, which means that the present letter could have been written on Thursday, 5 or Friday, 6 January 1882.</p>
                    	</note>
                    
                    
                    
